members.name: getLastVibrationFrequency
members.comment: Gets the last vibration frequency of this sensor. Different activities detected by the sensor will produce different frequencies and dictate the output of connected comparators.

members.name: setLastVibrationFrequency
members.comment: Sets the last vibration frequency of this sensor. Different activities detected by the sensor will produce different frequencies and dictate the output of connected comparators.
